[
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_fei_qing",
    "speaker_name": "陆菲青",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "姓陆的还不致于这么不要脸，去给满清鞑子做鹰犬。你们要拿我这几根老骨头去升官发财，嘿嘿，请来拿吧！",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 51,
    "line_end": 51
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_fei_qing",
    "speaker_name": "陆菲青",
    "listener": "char_li_yuan_zhi",
    "text": "沅芷，你我师生三年，总算相处不错。我本以为缘份已尽，那知还要碰头。我这件事性命攸关，你能守口如瓶，一句不漏吗？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 23,
    "line_end": 23
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_fei_qing",
    "speaker_name": "陆菲青",
    "listener": "char_li_yuan_zhi",
    "text": "令尊的所作所为，老实说我是大大的不以为然，将来你长大成人，盼你明辨是非，分得清好歹。你拜我为师，就须严守师门戒条，可做得到吗？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 103,
    "line_end": 103
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huo_qing_tong",
    "speaker_name": "霍青桐",
    "listener": "char_li_yuan_zhi",
    "text": "我是回部霍青桐。喂，我问你，咱们河水不犯井水，干么你硬给镖局子撑腰，坏我们的事？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_fei_qing",
    "speaker_name": "陆菲青",
    "listener": "char_huo_qing_tong",
    "text": "比剑比不过算得什么，圣经抢不回来才教丢脸呢。一个人的胜负荣辱打什么紧？全族给人家欺侮，那才须得拚命。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 39,
    "line_end": 39
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_fei_qing",
    "speaker_name": "陆菲青",
    "listener": "char_wen_tai_lai",
    "text": "我这师弟自甘下流，真是我师门之耻，但他武功精纯，而且千里迢迢从北京西来，必定还有后援。现下文老弟身受重伤，我看眼前只有避他一避，然后我们再约好手，跟他一决雌雄。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 163,
    "line_end": 163
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yu_yu_tong",
    "speaker_name": "余鱼同",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "在下行不改姓，坐不改名，姓余名鱼同。余者，人未之余。鱼者，混水摸鱼之鱼也。同者，君子和而不同之同，非破铜烂铁之铜也。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 95,
    "line_end": 95
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wen_tai_lai",
    "speaker_name": "文泰来",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "文某岂是贪生怕死之徒？躲在这般的地方，便是逃得性命，也落得天下英雄耻笑。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhou_zhong_ying",
    "speaker_name": "周仲英",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "英雄好汉是这样做的么？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 91,
    "line_end": 91
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_luo_bing",
    "speaker_name": "骆冰",
    "listener": "char_zhou_zhong_ying",
    "text": "你这沽名钓誉、狼心狗肺的老贼！你们害我丈夫，我跟你这老贼拚了。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 73,
    "line_end": 73
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yu_yu_tong",
    "speaker_name": "余鱼同",
    "listener": "char_luo_bing",
    "text": "咱们想法子救人要紧，先救四哥，再烧铁胆庄。",
    "tone": "焦急",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 75,
    "line_end": 75
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhou_qi",
    "speaker_name": "周绮",
    "listener": "char_chen_jia_luo",
    "text": "我弟弟还只十岁，他不懂事，把你们文爷的藏身地方说了出来。爹爹回到家来，大怒之下，失手把弟弟打死了，把我妈妈也气走了，这总对得起你们了吧？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_chen_jia_luo",
    "speaker_name": "陈家洛",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "周老英雄对红花会的好处，咱们至死不忘。各位兄弟，现下救火要紧。大家快动手。",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 11,
    "line_end": 11
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_luo_bing",
    "speaker_name": "骆冰",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "老当家临终之时，召集内三堂外三堂正副香主，遗命要少舵主接任总舵主。他说这并不是他有私心，只因此事是汉家光复的关键所在，要紧之至。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 93,
    "line_end": 93
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wen_tai_lai",
    "speaker_name": "文泰来",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你们这批给朝廷做走狗的奴才，文大爷落在你们手中，自有人给我报仇。瞧你们这些狼心狗肺的东西，有什么下场。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 83,
    "line_end": 83
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhang_zhao_zhong",
    "speaker_name": "张召重",
    "listener": "char_yu_yu_tong",
    "text": "好好一个年轻人，竟然自甘下流。文泰来是你什么人？干么这般舍命救他！",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 105,
    "line_end": 105
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_fei_qing",
    "speaker_name": "陆菲青",
    "listener": "char_zhang_zhao_zhong",
    "text": "你身已受伤，这里红花会众英雄全体到场，还有铁胆庄周老英雄出头相助，你今日想逃脱性命，这叫难上加难。你虽无情，我不能无义，念在当年恩师份上，我指点你一条生路。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 289,
    "line_end": 289
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhou_qi",
    "speaker_name": "周绮",
    "listener": "char_xu_tian_hong",
    "text": "你不会给刀砍伤？哼，说这样的满话！",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 97,
    "line_end": 97
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhou_qi",
    "speaker_name": "周绮",
    "listener": "char_xu_tian_hong",
    "text": "胡说！那有好端端的人叫小玫瑰的？",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 63,
    "line_end": 63
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_chen_jia_luo",
    "speaker_name": "陈家洛",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "咱们第一步要查知文四哥的所在。请马大哥继续派遣得力兄弟，往各衙门打探，今晚再请道长、五哥、六哥到巡抚衙门去瞧瞧。最要紧是别打草惊蛇，无论如何不能伸手动武。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qian_long",
    "speaker_name": "乾隆",
    "listener": "char_chen_jia_luo",
    "text": "兄台真是雅人，仓卒之间，安排得如此周到。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 161,
    "line_end": 161
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_chen_jia_luo",
    "speaker_name": "陈家洛",
    "listener": "char_qian_long",
    "text": "仁兄惠然肯来，幸何如之！",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 157,
    "line_end": 157
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qian_long",
    "speaker_name": "乾隆",
    "listener": "char_chen_jia_luo",
    "text": "兄台相招，岂能不来？",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 157,
    "line_end": 157
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_luo_bing",
    "speaker_name": "骆冰",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "李可秀关住大哥，咱们先杀了他小老婆。总舵主，你许不许？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_chen_jia_luo",
    "speaker_name": "陈家洛",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "各位哥哥，咱们只好先退出杭州。眼下四哥尚未救出，跟清兵接硬仗没好处。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_chen_jia_luo",
    "speaker_name": "陈家洛",
    "listener": "char_li_ke_xiu",
    "text": "怕死的也不来了，今天对不住，我们要带了文四爷一起走。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 39,
    "line_end": 39
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_chen_jia_luo",
    "speaker_name": "陈家洛",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "攻进提督府去，今日无论如何得把四哥找着。",
    "tone": "焦急",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 17,
    "line_end": 17
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wen_tai_lai",
    "speaker_name": "文泰来",
    "listener": "char_chen_jia_luo",
    "text": "总舵主你一人走吧，别管我。",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 137,
    "line_end": 137
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_chen_jia_luo",
    "speaker_name": "陈家洛",
    "listener": "char_qian_long",
    "text": "哥哥，你到今日还不认我么？",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 11,
    "line_end": 11
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guan_ming_mei",
    "speaker_name": "关明梅",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你们都见过小徒霍青桐，这事就由她身上而起。皇帝派兵去打回部，青桐的爸爸木卓伦领兵抵抗，敌不过清兵人多，连吃了几个败仗。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 187,
    "line_end": 187
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_chen_zheng_de",
    "speaker_name": "陈正德",
    "listener": "char_lu_fei_qing",
    "text": "哼，陆老弟，你的剑真是宝物！",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 185,
    "line_end": 185
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_luo_bing",
    "speaker_name": "骆冰",
    "listener": "char_yu_yu_tong",
    "text": "只要你以后好好给会里出力，再不对我无礼，今晚之事我绝不跟谁提起。以后我给你留心，帮你找一位才貌双全的好姑娘。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 115,
    "line_end": 115
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wen_tai_lai",
    "speaker_name": "文泰来",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我如何睡得着？",
    "tone": "焦急",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huo_qing_tong",
    "speaker_name": "霍青桐",
    "listener": "char_chen_jia_luo",
    "text": "你瞧，这就是他在山洞里学的武功。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 13,
    "line_end": 13
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiang_xiang_gong_zhu",
    "speaker_name": "香香公主",
    "listener": "char_chen_jia_luo",
    "text": "你说不怕，我就不怕。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiang_xiang_gong_zhu",
    "speaker_name": "香香公主",
    "listener": "char_chen_jia_luo",
    "text": "你十年不来，我等你十年；一辈子不来，我等你一辈子。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 77,
    "line_end": 77
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhang_zhao_zhong",
    "speaker_name": "张召重",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "回人送了一对玉瓶向皇上求和。玉瓶上画了一个回人古代女子，皇上大赞美艳，说当今之世决无如此人物。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 15,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhang_zhao_zhong",
    "speaker_name": "张召重",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "大将军，皇上差卑职到回疆来，有两件钦命，第一件就是拿刚才这女子进京。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 15,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_shi_xiao",
    "speaker_name": "袁士霄",
    "listener": "char_chen_jia_luo",
    "text": "这真是可遇不可求的奇缘。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 25,
    "line_end": 25
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guan_ming_mei",
    "speaker_name": "关明梅",
    "listener": "char_huo_qing_tong",
    "text": "这人喜新弃旧，你妹子又如此没姊妹之情。两人都该杀了。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huo_qing_tong",
    "speaker_name": "霍青桐",
    "listener": "char_guan_ming_mei",
    "text": "他⋯⋯他和我妹子好，我调兵的时候⋯⋯爹爹和大伙儿都疑我有私心。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_chen_zheng_de",
    "speaker_name": "陈正德",
    "listener": "char_guan_ming_mei",
    "text": "就是不吃这药，也死不了。",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guan_ming_mei",
    "speaker_name": "关明梅",
    "listener": "char_huo_qing_tong",
    "text": "你真造化，得了这灵丹妙药，就好得快了。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_shi_xiao",
    "speaker_name": "袁士霄",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "奸贼呀奸贼，凭你这身功夫，本来也是难得之极的了，若不是心地如此歹毒，我老头子忍不住要起爱才之心。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 103,
    "line_end": 103
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_chen_zheng_de",
    "speaker_name": "陈正德",
    "listener": "char_yuan_shi_xiao",
    "text": "袁大哥，我今日才当真对你佩服得五体投地。你徒儿已是如此，做兄弟的跟你可实在相差太远了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 15,
    "line_end": 15
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yu_yu_tong",
    "speaker_name": "余鱼同",
    "listener": "char_li_yuan_zhi",
    "text": "师妹，张召重那奸贼在哪里呀？",
    "tone": "焦急",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 233,
    "line_end": 233
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_fei_qing",
    "speaker_name": "陆菲青",
    "listener": "char_yu_yu_tong",
    "text": "这再好也没有，等将来你们大喜之日，再把两段金笛镶在一起。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 225,
    "line_end": 225
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_luo_bing",
    "speaker_name": "骆冰",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "陆伯伯，你的白龙剑没能拿上来，真可惜。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 45,
    "line_end": 45
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_chen_jia_luo",
    "speaker_name": "陈家洛",
    "listener": "char_qian_long",
    "text": "且不说六和塔中盟言如何，我们在海宁塘上曾击掌为誓，决不互相加害，你却用毒酒暗算于我，今日还有什么话说？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 261,
    "line_end": 261
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wen_tai_lai",
    "speaker_name": "文泰来",
    "listener": "char_chen_jia_luo",
    "text": "总舵主，你这次在回部学到了精妙武功，露几手给大家瞧瞧怎样？",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 81,
    "line_end": 81
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_chen_jia_luo",
    "speaker_name": "陈家洛",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "喀丝丽！喀丝丽！",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 392,
    "line_end": 392
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huo_qing_tong",
    "speaker_name": "霍青桐",
    "listener": "char_chen_jia_luo",
    "text": "咱们不能让妹子葬在这里。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 335,
    "line_end": 335
  }
]